s":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button\/tag(_:includeoptional:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"includeOptional","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" = true) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Hashable","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"tag","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value to use as the view’s tag.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"includeOptional","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the tag value for ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<V>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"also be set.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A view with the specified tag set.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to differentiate among certain selectable views,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like the possible values of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" or the tabs of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TabView"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Tag values can be of any type that conforms to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This modifier will write the tag value for the type ","type":"text"},{"code":"V","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", as well as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<V>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if ","type":"text"},{"code":"includeOptional","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is enabled. Containers checking for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags of either type will see the value as set.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In the example below, the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach","type":"reference"},{"text":" loop in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"text":" view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"builder iterates over the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Flavor"},{"text":" enumeration. It extracts the string","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of each enumeration element for use in constructing the row","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"label, and uses the enumeration value as input to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"tag(_:)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"modifier.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct FlavorPicker: View {","    enum Flavor: String, CaseIterable, Identifiable {","        case chocolate, vanilla, strawberry","        var id: Self { self }","    }","","    @State private var selectedFlavor: Flavor? = nil","","    var body: some View {","        Picker(\"Flavor\", selection: $selectedFlavor) {","            ForEach(Flavor.allCases) { flavor in","                Text(flavor.rawValue)","                    .tag(flavor)","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The selection type of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is an ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<Flavor>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and so it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will look for tags on its contents of ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<Flavor>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"type. Since the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tag modifier defaults to having ","type":"text"},{"code":"includeOptional","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" enabled, even though","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the tag for each option is a non-optional ","type":"text"},{"code":"Flavor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the tag modifier","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"writes values for both the non-optional, and optional versions of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value, allowing the contents to be selectable by the ","type":"text"},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically applies a default tag to each enumerated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"id"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter of the corresponding element. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the element’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"id"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter and the picker’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"selection"},{"type":"text","text":" input"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have exactly the same type, or the same type but optional, you can omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the explicit tag modifier."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To see examples that don’t require an explicit tag, see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui","type":"topic","title":"OpenSwiftUI","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declare the user interface and behavior for your app on every platform."}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Button":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Button","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/ForEach":{"abstract":[{"text":"A structure that computes views on demand from an underlying collection of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"identified data.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ForEach","kind":"identifie